headline: CoStar Group Founder and CEO Andy Florance Named 2025 Tech Titan by Washingtonian Magazine
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., September 16, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology, today announced that Founder and Chief Executive Officer Andy Florance has been named one of Washingtonian Magazine’s 2025 Tech Titans.
